                            <comment id="13219907" author="zjushch" created="Thu, 1 Mar 2012 08:30:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In the hbase-5501.patch, we prevent processing of SSH before finish assign ROOTandMETA,and use the same onlineServers for splitLog and joinCluster during initializing&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13220178" author="stack" created="Thu, 1 Mar 2012 17:43:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Whats going on here Chunhui?  You&apos;ve opened a new issue w/ same title as 5270?  How do they relate?  Shouldn&apos;t this patch be on 5270, not on this new issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13220180" author="stack" created="Thu, 1 Mar 2012 17:45:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is this patch right?  You have a disablessh flag.  What about other callbacks that could come in during the initialization?  I don&apos;t see where you queue up callbacks for processing post-initialization.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
